      <p class="eyebrow">P&L engineering × technical leverage</p>
      <h2>Every operating decision is a <strong>P&L</strong> decision.</h2>
      <p class="lede">Capital allocation is an engineering problem. Being a P&amp;L leader involves the discipline of turning technical work into margin, velocity, resilience, and option value. Here are the playbooks you need to produce the alpha you need to make returns above your operating baseline.</p>
