    <a class="stage-card" data-accent="green" id="ship" href="/frameworks/designed-convergence/">
      <span class="num green">04 Ship</span>
      <h3>Systems that converge by construction →</h3>
      <p>The goal is convergence by construction. Design the system so improvement is a mathematical property, not an aspiration. Ratcheted quality gates and graduated autonomy compress execution risk into something you can manage.</p>
